cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with machine learning and neural networks, which are typically categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses information theory and quantization, which fall under cs.IT (Information Theory). The experiments involve image classification, which is a common application of computer vision, falling under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper proposes a new learning framework that improves upon current state-of-the-art models, which is a common topic in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
